name: Nsw-art-films
tagline: Script to scrape the NSW Art Gallery film listings and upload to a Google Calendar.
body:
### Art Gallery of NSW film calendar

This is a web scraper I wrote in Perl to consolidate the Art Gallery of NSW's film calendar for easy viewing on a Google Calendar.

The calendar is available here: http://goo.gl/AtZP8C

If you notice anything missing shoot me an email at aidanb@gmail.com.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
